    <title>hexo 命令 fluid 配置 markdown 语法 指北</title>
    <link href="/hexo/2021-05/hello-world/"/>
    <url>/hexo/2021-05/hello-world/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <a href="https://hexo.io/">Hexo</a>!  Check <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/">documentation</a> for more info. <a href="https://fluid-dev.github.io/hexo-fluid-docs/guide/#%E5%AF%BC%E8%88%AA%E8%8F%9C%E5%8D%95">fluid</a></p><h2 id="Quick-Start"><a href="#Quick-Start" class="headerlink" title="Quick Start"></a>Quick Start</h2><h3 id="Create-a-new-post"><a href="#Create-a-new-post" class="headerlink" title="Create a new post"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ hexo new <span class="hljs-string">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html">Writing</a></p><h3 id="Generate-static-files"><a href="#Generate-static-files" class="headerlink" title="Generate static files"></a>Generate static files</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ hexo generate<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="clean"><a href="#clean" class="headerlink" title="clean"></a>clean</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ hexo clean<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Run-server"><a href="#Run-server" class="headerlink" title="Run server"></a>Run server</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ hexo server<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Deploy-to-remote-sites"><a href="#Deploy-to-remote-sites" class="headerlink" title="Deploy to remote sites"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><p>设置 [^1]</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs git">$ hexo deploy <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="hexo-支持的markdown特性"><a href="#hexo-支持的markdown特性" class="headerlink" title="hexo 支持的markdown特性"></a>hexo 支持的markdown特性</h3><p><mark>参考</mark></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown"><span class="xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">mark</span>&gt;</span></span>参考<span class="xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">mark</span>&gt;</span></span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="note note-success">            <p>文字 或者 <code>markdown</code> 均可 primary secondary success danger warning info light</p>          </div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">&#123;% note success %&#125;<br>文字 或者 <span class="hljs-code">`markdown`</span> 均可 primary secondary success danger warning info light<br>&#123;% endnote %&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><span class="label label-primary">text</span><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">&#123;% label primary @text %&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><a class="btn" href="url"  title="title" target="_blank">text</a><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">&#123;% btn url, text, title %&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>            <input type="checkbox" disabled checked="checked">text          <figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">&#123;% cb text, checked?, incline? %&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><ruby>饕餮 <rt>tāo tiè</rt></ruby> 是古代中国神话传说中的一种神秘怪物，别名叫 <ruby>狍鸮 <rt>páo xiāo</rt></ruby>，古书《山海经·北次二经》介绍其特点是：其形状如羊身人面，眼在腋下，虎齿人手</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown"><span class="xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">ruby</span>&gt;</span></span>饕餮 <span class="xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">rt</span>&gt;</span></span>tāo tiè<span class="xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">rt</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">ruby</span>&gt;</span></span> 是古代中国神话传说中的一种神秘怪物，别名叫 <span class="xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">ruby</span>&gt;</span></span>狍鸮 <span class="xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">rt</span>&gt;</span></span>páo xiāo<span class="xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">rt</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">ruby</span>&gt;</span></span>，古书《山海经·北次二经》介绍其特点是：其形状如羊身人面，眼在腋下，虎齿人手<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><del>长蛇座</del> <ins>半人马座</ins> </p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown"><span class="xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">del</span>&gt;</span></span>长蛇座<span class="xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">del</span>&gt;</span></span> <span class="xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">ins</span>&gt;</span></span>半人马座<span class="xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">ins</span>&gt;</span></span> <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="group-image-container"><div class="group-image-row"><div class="group-image-wrap"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/winningcn/PB/img/index_y.JPG"></div><div class="group-image-wrap"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/winningcn/PB/img/index_y.JPG"></div><div class="group-image-wrap"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/winningcn/PB/img/index_y.JPG"></div></div><div class="group-image-row"><div class="group-image-wrap"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/winningcn/PB/img/index_y.JPG"></div><div class="group-image-wrap"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/winningcn/PB/img/index_y.JPG"></div></div></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">&#123;% gi total 5 3-2 %&#125;<br>  ![](https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/winningcn/PB/img/index<span class="hljs-emphasis">_y.JPG)</span><br><span class="hljs-emphasis">  ![](https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/winningcn/PB/img/index_</span>y.JPG)<br>  ![](https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/winningcn/PB/img/index<span class="hljs-emphasis">_y.JPG)</span><br><span class="hljs-emphasis">  ![](https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/winningcn/PB/img/index_</span>y.JPG)<br>  ![](https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/winningcn/PB/img/index<span class="hljs-emphasis">_y.JPG)</span><br><span class="hljs-emphasis">&#123;% endgi %&#125;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>jsdeliver 静态图片</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">![<span class="hljs-string">banner_2</span>](<span class="hljs-link">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/winningcn/PB/img/banner_2.JPG</span>)<br>![<span class="hljs-string">inde_1</span>](<span class="hljs-link">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/winningcn/PB/img/inde_1.JPG</span>)<br>![<span class="hljs-string">inde_2</span>](<span class="hljs-link">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/winningcn/PB/img/inde_2.JPG</span>)<br>![<span class="hljs-string">avatar</span>](<span class="hljs-link">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/winningcn/PB/img/avatar.png</span>)<br>![<span class="hljs-string">index_b</span>](<span class="hljs-link">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/winningcn/PB/img/index_b.JPG</span>)<br>![<span class="hljs-string">favicon</span>](<span class="hljs-link">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/winningcn/PB/img/favicon.png</span>)<br>![<span class="hljs-string">index_x</span>](<span class="hljs-link">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/winningcn/PB/img/index_x.JPG</span>)<br>![<span class="hljs-string">index_d</span>](<span class="hljs-link">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/winningcn/PB/img/index_d.JPG</span>)<br>![<span class="hljs-string">index_p</span>](<span class="hljs-link">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/winningcn/PB/img/index_p.JPG</span>)<br>![<span class="hljs-string">index_y</span>](<span class="hljs-link">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/winningcn/PB/img/index_y.JPG</span>)<br>![<span class="hljs-string">loading</span>](<span class="hljs-link">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/winningcn/PB/img/loading.gif</span>)<br>![<span class="hljs-string">police_beian</span>](<span class="hljs-link">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/winningcn/PB/img/police_beian.png</span>)<br>![<span class="hljs-string">index_z</span>](<span class="hljs-link">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/winningcn/PB/img/index_z.JPG</span>)<br>![<span class="hljs-string">wechat_show</span>](<span class="hljs-link">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/winningcn/PB/img/wechat_show.png</span>)<br>![<span class="hljs-string">banner_1</span>](<span class="hljs-link">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/winningcn/PB/img/banner_1.png</span>)<br>![<span class="hljs-string">default</span>](<span class="hljs-link">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/winningcn/PB/img/default.png</span>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="git-tips"><a href="#git-tips" class="headerlink" title="git tips"></a>git tips</h3><p>如何删除 github 文件夹</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 步骤：（以删除.idea文件夹为例）</span><br><br>git rm -r --cached .idea  <span class="hljs-comment">#--cached不会把本地的.idea删除</span><br>git commit -m <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;delete .idea dir&#x27;</span><br>git push -u origin master<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如何撤消git rm</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 如果你已经提交更改，则：</span><br><br>git reset (--hard) HEAD~1  <span class="hljs-comment">#彻底回退到指定commit-id的状态，暂存区和工作区也会变为指定commit-id版本的内容</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 如果不是那么：</span><br><br>git reset<br>git checkout -- $(git ls-files -d)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>git 本地远端 对齐</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git pull --rebase origin master<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 再次执行</span><br>git push origin master<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/31443926">上传github仓库主分支一般步骤</a></p><h3 id="更新"><a href="#更新" class="headerlink" title="更新"></a>更新</h3><p>2021-5-31 about 页面 增加播放器，增加<a href="https://60minutejs.vercel.app/BMI-Calculator/index.html">BMI</a> 计算，hexo 的 injector.js 一定要放在 \hexo\themes\fluid\scripts 目录下。</p><h3 id="Todo"><a href="#Todo" class="headerlink" title="Todo"></a>Todo</h3><p><a href="https://xiejilu.com/2020/04/23/hexo-pwa/">给 Hexo 博客添加 PWA 支持 </a><br><a href="https://blog.2to.fun/post/hexo-injector/">HEXO INJECTOR</a></p><h3 id="for-ref"><a href="#for-ref" class="headerlink" title="for ref"></a>for ref</h3><p><a href="https://wizardforcel.gitbooks.io/markdown-simple-world/content/hexo-tutor-1.html">hexo how to</a><br><a href="https://erenship.com/posts/40222.html#****">fluid customization</a><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_36264495/article/details/112448622">hexo的fluid主题添加瀑布流懒加载相册功能</a><br><a href="https://github.com/521xueweihan/git-tips">git-tips</a><br><a href="http://caibaojian.com/css3/appendix/color-keywords.htm">css color keywords</a><br>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html">Deployment</a></p><p><mark>参考</mark><br>[^1]  配置git</p>]]></content>
    
    
